special_powers.name: BATTLEFIELD PROMOTION: RISE
special_powers.description: When Batman hits one or more opposing characters, after actions resolve, place a Promotion Token on his character card. You may then roll a d6 that can't be rerolled and add 1 for each Promotion Token on his character card; on a result of 8 or higher, replace this character with D10A #023 Batman on the same click number.

special_powers.name: BATTLEFIELD PROMOTION: RISE
special_powers.description: When Wonder Woman hits one or more opposing characters, after actions resolve, place a Promotion Token on her character card. You may then roll a d6 that can't be rerolled and add 1 for each Promotion Token on her character card; on a result of 8 or higher, replace this character with D10A #022 Wonder Woman on the same click number.

special_powers.name: BATTLEFIELD PROMOTION: MARTIAN MANHUNTER
special_powers.description: When John Jones hits one or more opposing characters, after actions resolve, place a Promotion Token on his character card. You may then roll a d6 that can't be rerolled and add 1 for each Promotion Token on his character card; on a result of 8 or higher, replace this character with D10A #019 Martian Manhunter a number of clicks from its blue starting line equal to the number of clicks this character is from its starting line. On a result of 10 or higher, replace this character on the same click number.

special_powers.name: CONSTRUCT
special_powers.description: Green Lantern begins the game without the Construct.  Green Lantern can use Barrier.  When he does, attach the Construct to him after actions resolve and he may make a close combat attack targeting a character adjacent to a square with one of these Barrier markers in it as a free action.  When the Construct is attached, Green Lantern can use Energy Shield/Deflection and Close Combat Expert.  When Green Lantern takes damage or uses Close Combat Expert, remove the Construct.

special_powers.name: IN BRIGHTEST DAY
special_powers.description: During your turn, hindering terrain within 6 squares of Green Lantern is considered clear terrain for line of fire purposes.

special_powers.name: BATTLEFIELD PROMOTION: BRAINIAC
special_powers.description: When Brainiac hits one or more opposing characters, after actions resolve, place a Promotion Token on his character card. You may then roll a d6 that can't be rerolled and add 1 for each Promotion Token on his character card; on a result of 8 or higher, replace this character with D10A #012 Brainiac a number of clicks from its blue starting line equal to the number of clicks this character is from its starting line. One a result of 10 or higher, replace this character on the same click number.

special_powers.name: BATTLEFIELD PROMOTION: ORACLE
special_powers.description: When Batgirl hits one or more opposing characters, after actions resolve, place a Promotion Token on her character card. You may then roll a d6 that can't be rerolled and add 1 for each Promotion Token on her character card; on a result of 8 or higher, replace this character with D10A #017 Oracle on the same click number.

special_powers.name: A LEADER ON ANY TEAM
special_powers.description: Nightwing is a wild card.  During your first turn, choose a friendly character's keyword; Nightwing possesses that keyword for the rest of the game.  Nightwing can use Leadership, but only removes action tokens from characters using a team ability that Nightwing can use.

special_powers.name: BATTLEFIELD PROMOTION: CATWOMAN
special_powers.description: When Catwoman hits one or more opposing characters, after actions resolve, place a Promotion Token on her character card.  You may then roll a d6 that can't be rerolled and add 1 for each Promotion Token on her character card; on a result of 8 or higher, replace this character with d10a #015 Catwoman on the same click number.

special_powers.name: THE SCARAB
special_powers.description: The first time in a game when Blue Beetle would take 3 or more damage from an attack, instead he does not take damage and is given an action token.

special_powers.name: THE SCARAB AWAKENED
special_powers.description: At the beginning of your turn, roll a d6.  On a result of 5-6, until your next turn, Blue Beetle modifies his attack value by +2, can use Blades/Claws/Fangs and possesses Battle Fury.

special_powers.name: DIMENSIONAL PERCEPTION
special_powers.description: Blue Beetle can use Probability Control, but only for attack rolls where he is the attacker or a target of the attack.

special_powers.name: SO FAST YOU DIDN'T SEE THE HITS
special_powers.description: The Flash can use Charge and Flurry.  When The Flash uses Charge, he can use Exploit Weakness.

special_powers.name: MACH 3 PUNCH
special_powers.description: Damage dealt by Flash cannot be reduced below 1.

special_powers.name: BATTLEFIELD PROMOTION: PASS THE TORCH
special_powers.description: When Green Lantern hits one or more opposing characters, after actions resolve, place a Promotion Token on his character card.  You may then roll a d6 that can't be rerolled and add 1 for each Promotion Token on his character card; on a result of 8 or higher, replace this character with D10A #004 Green Lantern on the same click number.

special_powers.name: IMPOSSIBLE TO PLAN AGAINST
special_powers.description: Opposing forces subtract one from their action total if not reduced by any other effect.

special_powers.name: MY SHIP AND I ARE ONE
special_powers.description: Give Brainiac a double power action and place him in any square within his speed value. After actions resolve, you may give Brainiac a close combat or ranged combat action as a free action.

special_powers.name: I'LL SHOW YOU IMPERVIOUS
special_powers.description: Brainiac can use Impervious. When turning the dial, if this click is revealed due to damage taken from an opponent's attack, stop turning the dial. This power cannot be countered or ignored.

special_powers.name: MASTER MANIPULATOR
special_powers.description: Brainiac can use Perplex. When he does, he can only target friendly characters and they can be anywhere on the map.

special_powers.name: BATTLEFIELD PROMOTION: LEX LUTHOR
special_powers.description: When Lex Luthor hits one or more opposing characters, after actions resolve, place a Promotion Token on his character card. You may then roll a d6 that can't be rerolled and add 1 for each Promotion Token on his character card; on a result of 8 or higher, replace this character with D10A #020 Lex Luthor a number of clicks from its blue starting line equal to the number of clicks this character is from its starting line. On a result of 10 or higher, replace this character on the same click number.

special_powers.name: BATTLEFIELD PROMOTION: NIGHTWING
special_powers.description: When Robin hits one or more opposing characters, after actions resolve, place a Promotion Token on his character card. You may then roll a d6 that can't be rerolled and add 1 for each Promotion Token on his character card; on a result of 8 or higher, replace this character with D10A #007 Nightwing on the same click number.

special_powers.name: BAD LUCK WHEN I CROSS YOUR PATH
special_powers.description: Other characters within 6 squares of Catwoman assigned a relic or a resource can't use the effects of the relic or resource.

special_powers.name: BURGLAR
special_powers.description: Catwoman can use Leap/Climb and Stealth.

special_powers.name: BATTLEFIELD PROMOTION: PASS THE TORCH
special_powers.description: When Blue Beetle hits one or more opposing characters, after actions resolve, place a Promotion Token on his character card. You may then roll a d6 that can't be rerolled and add 1 for each Promotion Token on his character card; on a result of 8 or higher, replace this character with D10A #009 Blue Beetle on the same click number.

special_powers.name: MY EYES ARE EVERYWHERE
special_powers.description: If Oracle is not adjacent to an opposing character and is either in her starting area or on elevated terrain, she can draw lines of fire and count range and squares from the square of any single friendly character that has the Batman Family, Birds of Prey or Justice League keyword.

special_powers.name: THE MYSTERY OF THE ORACLE
special_powers.description: Give Oracle a power action and choose Outwit, Perplex, or Probability Control. She can use the chosen power until the beginning of her next turn.

special_powers.name: BATTLEFIELD PROMOTION: PASS THE TORCH
special_powers.description: When The Flash hits one or more opposing characters, after actions resolve, place a Promotion Token on his character card. You may then roll a d6 that can't be rerolled and add 1 for each Promotion Token on his character card; on a result of 8 or higher, replace this character with D10A #010 Flash on the same click number.

special_powers.name: EMBRACING MY HERITAGE
special_powers.description: When Martian Manhunter has zero action tokens, he can use Shape Change.

special_powers.name: MARTIAN PHYSIOLOGY
special_powers.description: Martian Manhunter can use Stealth and Charge.  When Martian Manhunter uses Charge he can ignore blocking terrain as he moves.

special_powers.name: I SEE THE ATTACK IN YOUR MIND
special_powers.description: Martian Manhunter can use Super Senses.

special_powers.name: PART OF MY PERSONAL INVENTORY
special_powers.description: Once per game, give Lex Luthor a power action to place a special object whose name includes "Kryptonite" from outside the game into an adjacent square.

special_powers.name: BOOM TUBE SNEAK ATTACK
special_powers.description: Lex Luthor can use Phasing/Teleport. When he does, after actions resolve, if he moved half his speed value or less, he may be given a ranged combat action as a free action.

special_powers.name: MY HATRED WILL NEVER DIE, ALIEN!
special_powers.description: Lex Luthor deals penetrating damage to characters that possess the Superman Ally team ability or the Kryptonian keyword.

special_powers.name: BATTLEFIELD PROMOTION: RISE
special_powers.description: When Superman hits one or more opposing characters, after actions resolve, place a Promotion Token on his character card. You may then roll a d6 that can't be rerolled and add 1 for each Promotion Token on his character card; on a result of 8 or higher, replace this character with D10A #024 Superman on the same click number.

special_powers.name: EMPOWERED BY BATTLE
special_powers.description: Whenever an opposing character within 4 squares rolls a 1 or 2 for a Super Senses roll, you may heal Wonder Woman 1 damage.

special_powers.name: BLACK LASSO
special_powers.description: Wonder Woman can use Incapacitate as if she had a range value of 6. When she does, instead of giving a hit target an action token, you may place that character adjacent to Wonder Woman and may make a close combat attack as a free action targeting the placed character.

special_powers.name: EMPOWERED BY DECEPTION
special_powers.description: When an opposing character within 4 squares rolls a 1 or 2 for a Shape Change roll, you may heal Batman of 1 damage.

special_powers.name: RISE
special_powers.description: Batman can use Stealth and Leap/Climb.

special_powers.name: RAIN OF BLACK RINGS
special_powers.description: Batman can use Pulse Wave as if he had a range value of 8. When he does, friendly characters that share a keyword with Batman reduce damage dealt to them to 0.

special_powers.name: EMPOWERED BY DESPAIR
special_powers.description: Whenever an opposing character rolls a 1 or 2 for a Leadership roll, you may heal Superman 1 damage.

special_powers.name: YOU FIGHT ME AS IF I LIVE
special_powers.description: Superman can use Regeneration and Toughness. This power can't be countered.
